### 1) Complete upload
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/videos/upload/complete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "uploader_ref": "demo_user_1",
  "filename": "breaking_fire_news.mp4",
  "content_type": "video/mp4",
  "storage_uri": "s3://demo/breaking_fire_news.mp4"
}

### 2) Run phase A
# POST /api/v1/workflow/{job_id}/phase-a

### 3) Create gate 1 task
# POST /api/v1/workflow/{job_id}/gate-1/create

### 4) Approve gate 1 task
# POST /api/v1/reviews/tasks/{task_id}/decision

### 5) Handle gate 1
# POST /api/v1/workflow/{job_id}/gate-1/handle

### 6) Create gate 2 task
# POST /api/v1/workflow/{job_id}/gate-2/create

### 7) Approve gate 2 task
# POST /api/v1/reviews/tasks/{task_id}/decision

### 8) Finalize
# POST /api/v1/workflow/{job_id}/finalize

